data.description: Gorgeous waterfront home located at the end of a cul-de-sac overlooks the golf course. Spectacular view of nature and various types of birds while relaxing on the patio and pool. The house has two living areas, large spacious master bedroom located downstairs with access to the patio. The kitchen has granite top with oak cabinets.  The master bath has separate shower, with double  vanity and spa tub.  A second bedroom and full bath located downstairs. Upstairs are 2 spacious bedrooms, Bonus room to use for entertainment and additional full bath. Most closets have built in shelving for organization.
